**Summary:** Documents the User Mapping (Aliasing) API that maps different user IDs to a global user ID across projects in Amplitude's Portfolio add-on, using POST requests to `/usermap` endpoint with `user_id`, `global_user_id`, and optional `unmap` parameters.

